{"tid":1141174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber司機遭市民舉報今認非法取酬 官指涉龐大集團操縱可考慮判監","createTime":"2019-05-06T10:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T14:22:39.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"21bbe605fd5b7707f1ebae4567f4fbc22396b0a9","tid":1141174,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lsgx1cF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsgx1cF.png&h=5157636c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n認罪被告李兆華(勞東來攝)(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n政府大力打擊Uber共享乘車服務，不少司機因而被控。東區裁判法院今處理30宗Uber司機涉非法載客取酬案件，其中一名司機認罪。惟裁判官罕見地並非直接罰款了事，反稱案件有別於一兩人單獨行事的白牌車個案，而是涉及龐大集團安排或操縱，而被告參與其中，遂詢問辯方律師：「即使初犯，判刑嘅時候係咪都可以考慮坐監？」最終裁判官聽取求情後，決定先為被告索閱社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今天處理的30宗案件全是市民乘搭後舉報，而非警方放蛇後作拘控。<br />\n<br />\n被告李兆華（33歲）去年9月12日駕駛Tesla汽車，接載一位乘客由嘉亨灣前往藍灣半島，及後遭舉報。他在庭外稱對判刑不太擔心，「都OK嘅」，認罪是因為不想拖延下去。他透露，Uber會安排律師協助答辯。律師求情指被告初犯，任職文員，兼職駕駛Uber賺外快。<br />\n<br />\n對於主任裁判官羅德泉指案件由大集團操縱，律師稱被告以加盟形式駕駛Uber，涉案車程短短十分鐘，沒資料證實被告全數享有約78元車資。由於目前有Uber案件正在上訴，被告眼中Uber服務是否合法，存在灰色地帶，不像盜竊或藏毒一樣明顯違法，認為裁判官可考慮先索取報告，了解被告犯案原因。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官押後到5月20日判刑。其餘29宗案件則押後至7月29日再訊，等候高等法院頒佈對同類案件的上訴裁決。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：ESCC584-607, 1022-1025, 1027, 1030/19】<br />\n記者 勞東來"},{"pid":"606bb104ca64687cf5352ee7e8e324eac656a4c7","tid":1141174,"uid":47202,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"個官係咪揸住幾十個的士牌係手？"},{"pid":"64abc43c8d17fecf8c38c3bca40ab94599790289","tid":1141174,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"uber淪為即用即棄產物"},{"pid":"137a10666b61b68f079d2110130b0e878e6205d7","tid":1141174,"uid":118677,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"&quot;遭市民舉報&quot;<br />\n咪即係的士狗囉"},{"pid":"8e2b56663500255d2af318978cbe48c8a4a593df","tid":1141174,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c78c427cf380cdea9dbc1f1803a3c41548bb19","tid":1141174,"uid":9542,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"一間公司就叫龐大集團，d 的士狗叫咩，仲撚似犯罪組織添呀"},{"pid":"8ac8165bf768f746c5873b5310e33e2c6104aaf7","tid":1141174,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"龐大集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大組織罪行點解唔拉主腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f094c12287f81f06909ff6f4a5cf54839dcc99d0","tid":1141174,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606bb104ca64687cf5352ee7e8e324eac656a4c7","tid":1141174,"uid":47202,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"個官係咪揸住幾十個的士牌係手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"事實係犯法 只可以係政府修例"},{"pid":"4f5e23a1008e5cafb65d330da7d00e0dfb576063","tid":1141174,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"出架VAN仔仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb8e91d61edca5ef62700b36c3345fa59667a0a","tid":1141174,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔明 咁短程都要78蚊,點解唔搭的士"},{"pid":"292806ed82d249c3e2e39b6add58370315df1ea4","tid":1141174,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdb8e91d61edca5ef62700b36c3345fa59667a0a","tid":1141174,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔明 咁短程都要78蚊,點解唔搭的士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"因為的士狗係狗?"},{"pid":"eda6812f38b8fffa82f9c8aaec80770ce6f9124c","tid":1141174,"uid":62755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:15:14.000Z","msg":"仆街想焗人坐的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧願轉幾程地鐵都唔撚坐的士"},{"pid":"dab3286fe3ed401023ad224fd84b4282cf42fd1f","tid":1141174,"uid":189638,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bdb8e91d61edca5ef62700b36c3345fa59667a0a","tid":1141174,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔明 咁短程都要78蚊,點解唔搭的士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"其實Uber X 未出之前，uber 係貴過的貴都有幾成。<br />\n所以好多人搭車唔係只諗錢，服務都好重要，的士狗就係太狗。<br />\n<br />\n講白啲就係的士狗服務差、又串，遠又嫌遠、近又嫌近、過海又唔去、限制多多，仲要串過馬撚、態度又差，揸車玩命（鳩CUT線、硬CUT線）、又唔找錢、啲數永遠唔清唔楚，仲要勁多黑的、專劏人。<br />\n<br />\n公平啲講係牌主迫成咁，所以之前好多揸的士嘅轉揸咗UBER<br />\n<br />\nUber 之前嘅好處、明碼實價、好多新車、司機有禮好多、幾個人評得佢差就冇得做。唔洗用現金、唔洗找錢、時間好預計、CALL車，幾多分鐘係邊到等，等車時間通常唔會好耐"},{"pid":"1f2f67b59f22deb804686668bbf1cd5ba51902f8","tid":1141174,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢類相關post都係 屌政府 屌dc9<br />\n佢地固然pk<br />\n但之前睇過一單case study之後有咗更多睇法<br />\n單case係講 uber喺new york點插旗<br />\n一開始都係非非地法<br />\n坐大之後 利益團體&amp;政府就打壓<br />\n但跟住市民瘋狂去信 議員&amp;媒體 shift咗個public opinions<br />\n之後先正式合法化<br />\n<br />\n香港地唔知係市民表達意見唔夠（無理由呀 投訴之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n定係 媒體方面太廢<br />\n定係 議會其實唔多聆聽市民聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5818a9bd111e9c91842133e1e0adc7912640ec3f","tid":1141174,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2f67b59f22deb804686668bbf1cd5ba51902f8","tid":1141174,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢類相關post都係 屌政府 屌dc9<br />\n佢地固然pk<br />\n但之前睇過一單case study之後有咗更多睇法<br />\n單case係講 uber喺new york點插旗<br />\n一開始都係非非地法<br />\n坐大之後 利益團體&amp;政府就打壓<br />\n但跟住市民瘋狂去信 議員&amp;媒體 shift咗個public opinions<br />\n之後先正式合法化<br />\n<br />\n香港地唔知係市民表達意見唔夠（無理由呀 投訴之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n定係 媒體方面太廢<br />\n定係 議會其實唔多聆聽市民聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"係香港政府當民意 on9"},{"pid":"fd1a9ef52d9de566207648bf181c9abe258c0ba1","tid":1141174,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"a426568ad866fc53b8d1e78b7b8eaaaef338684a","tid":1141174,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"咩人搭完會報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f29a3002ef868028b705f34aafb08c237c253d3","tid":1141174,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a426568ad866fc53b8d1e78b7b8eaaaef338684a","tid":1141174,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"咩人搭完會報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"DC9"},{"pid":"13b64af791eae4bfba901fa2a72ac4b361a549e0","tid":1141174,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f29a3002ef868028b705f34aafb08c237c253d3","tid":1141174,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a426568ad866fc53b8d1e78b7b8eaaaef338684a","tid":1141174,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"咩人搭完會報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"DC9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"DC9"},{"pid":"92ac477abe83916c1c6d546c5efd9421656da097","tid":1141174,"uid":126566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"Dlllm uber不知幾好 去過外國用就知<br />\n係香港成日夜晚坐的士<br />\n係尖沙咀去返九龍 個個都話近唔去<br />\n試過兩個人 係尖沙咀個到搵左成粒鐘的士先有<br />\n到係香港去九龍 10架有10架的士都話唔想去九龍<br />\n乜7香港車唔識九龍路 做唔到生意<br />\n屌你咩 香港呢家幾撚大呀 你唔識路唔識裝gps 外國 台灣都有啦 我呢家係坐的士呀 仲要俾人簡地方 <br />\n屌 寧願俾貴啲坐uber好過 仲未計的士成日兜路 割客 香港根本可以唔洗坐的士 地鐵又開得夜 巴士有n車 仲有紅van 你出旺角實有車返到屋企 唔好俾我聽到咩的士呢家唔好賺 係你地搞L成架"},{"pid":"cb5803d403cca5825c3a409aadc8b9d3fa4f4ea3","tid":1141174,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5818a9bd111e9c91842133e1e0adc7912640ec3f","tid":1141174,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2f67b59f22deb804686668bbf1cd5ba51902f8","tid":1141174,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢類相關post都係 屌政府 屌dc9<br />\n佢地固然pk<br />\n但之前睇過一單case study之後有咗更多睇法<br />\n單case係講 uber喺new york點插旗<br />\n一開始都係非非地法<br />\n坐大之後 利益團體&amp;政府就打壓<br />\n但跟住市民瘋狂去信 議員&amp;媒體 shift咗個public opinions<br />\n之後先正式合法化<br />\n<br />\n香港地唔知係市民表達意見唔夠（無理由呀 投訴之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n定係 媒體方面太廢<br />\n定係 議會其實唔多聆聽市民聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"係香港政府當民意 on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"因為珠姐"},{"pid":"a0189c6ec9e54204344137972613aaebe0e77319","tid":1141174,"uid":3078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"龐大集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠唔夠痰餵豬大先"},{"pid":"005c662e41a081fab6cc83067fd4e7d7d2a8c782","tid":1141174,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2f7a3f4b5984062623e9e423e809f599cfe56f1b","tid":1141174,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"好彩蛇頭走得快好世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}